<div class="home-page-top">
  <table class="table-center"><tr><td>
    <div class="text-box">
      <h1>Give your customers a <span class="color2">great</span> first impression.</h1>
    </div>
  </td></tr></table>
</div>
<div class="full-width-col">
  Your website will be the first impression of your business for most customers. I create positive experiences for the viewers of your website, bringing you <span class="color1 bold">more customers.</span>
</div>
<div class="full-width-col color1-bg">
  <h1>1-up the competition. Make sure your website is:</h1>
</div>
<div class="row features">
  <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
    <div class="box">
        <%= image_tag 'maintainable.svg', class: 'icon-img' %>
        <h1 class="center">Maintainable</h1>
        Having a web designer maintain all your website's information can be expensive. Manage content yourself through a CMS with an easy to use interface.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
    <div class="box">
        <%= image_tag 'responsive.svg', class: 'icon-img' %>
        <h1 class="center">Responsive</h1>
        Half of internet users are on a mobile device. It is critical for your website to function just as well on mobile devices as it does on desktops.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-0">
    <div class="box">
        <%= image_tag 'appealing.svg', class: 'icon-img' %>
        <h1 class="center">Appealing</h1>
        Keep your customers on your website by making sure it's nice to look at.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="home-page-bottom">
  <table class="table-center"><tr><th>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
        <div class="call-to-action">
          Interested?<br>
          <button class="btn btn-lg btn-primary">Tell us about your project.</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </th></tr></table>
</div>